title: The Sims 4 with Get Together and Everything Before ALL IN ONE
description:
Hi there! This is an ALL IN ONE new installer that I have put together.

It should save you space and time!

No more need to install the packs one by one!

I really hope you like this new release and can use it.

Instructions at(YouTube)



CONTENT INCLUDED

    The Sims 4 (Base Game)
    Get to Work
    Get Together
    Outdoor Retreat
    Spa Day
    Luxury Party Stuff
    Perfect Patio Stuff
    Cool Kitchen Stuff
    Spooky Stuff
    Digital Deluxe Upgrade
    Holiday Celebration Pack



CONTENT NOT INCLUDED (YET)

    Kids Room Stuff
    Dine Out
    Romantic Garden Stuff
    Movie Hangout Stuff
